    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>An absorbent paper or board, made from several sheets moistened and pasted together, used for making moulds for casting printing plates and stereotypes.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
